(2749, 1, '2015-10-12 13:40:48', '2015-10-12 13:40:48', '[row]\r\n\r\n[span12]\r\n\r\nYan International strives to help its customers succeed by supplying finest quality ingredients and specialty something foods. Our goal is to maintain outstanding service to help our customers achieve their goals.\r\nWe go the extra mile to enhance our customer experience. Our customer is our best friend; we fuse strong and enduring connections—with business partners and the communities in which we live in.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p class="ewrw">I believe in delighting the customer with service. I believe in the finest quality ingredients. I believe in the health benefits of the Mediterranean diet. That is why I founded Yan International to combine my passion for service and quality with healthy diet.</p>\r\nRegardless how large we grow, I keep it as my personal mission to develop a close relationship with my clients to adapt to their needs. I do not believe in minimum orders. I believe in next day service. I believe customer needs change by the day and flexibility is key to serve their needs.\r\n\r\nProtecting the environment is important to me. At Yan International we minimize our carbon footprint by using recycled packaging and containers. .\r\n\r\n<img class="aligncenter wp-image-2052 size-full" src="http://yanin.shahum.net/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/blog1-1.jpg" alt="blog1-1" width="1600" height="1200" />\r\n\r\n[/span12]\r\n\r\n[/row]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1797-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-10-12 13:40:48', '2015-10-12 13:40:48', '', 1797, 'http://yanin.shahum.net/uncategorized/1797-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
